1. What is an Exception
-> Exception ka matlab hai disruptive event matlab kuch galat hojana code me and wo galti kem karan
hamra code ye bolta hai ki ye se aab aage nhai bhada jaeyga flow ko inpterupt ho chuka hai
isko handle karo or system ko batao ki iss error ko aise handel karo and hamra programm ka flow
tode na chalne de ...
-> uppar wala jo error ko handel kar raha hai usi ko ham bolte hai exception handling
-> Exception ek taraha ka object hi hai jaise apan ne dheka ta ki array ke andar hamra error
aaya tha to terminal me error aaya tha with name of array index of bound exception in it throw
kiya tha java me exception hamrai galti pe is error me hamko exception ki type batai jati hai
kya type tha and bhot kuch .
-> chart ke andar throwable hai usme do chiz hai ERROR and EXCEPTION
-> ERROR ye apni galti ke karan nhai hota ye hota system ke galti ke karan jaise memory full
hojana and system ke kuch issue ke karan se hota hai isme hamara koi haat nhai hota .
-> EXCEPTION ye apni galti ke karan hota hai jaise khai pe error aana ye hamne galat logic
lhik diya ho uske wjaha iske do type hai runtime exception and compile time exception .

2. Try-Catch
-> Try-Catch iska matlab hai ki hamko pata hai ki esme error ane wali to wo error handel kaise karna
hai wo try-catch ki madat se handel karenge jise ham bolte hai exception handling .
-> try ke andar jo bhi ham lhikte hai wo exception aane ki shambhavna rehti hai agar code me
exception aajaye to java direct exception throw na kare isliye ham catch ka use karenge catch(Arti
hmatcException exception){sout("gadbad hogai")} iska matlab hai ki agar mera try ka code me exception
aaya to me catch me jo bhi lhikunga wo chal jaeyga and catch ke andar ham aapna exception ko
handle kar rhae honge .